Package: scdcLISA
Type: Package
Title: Spatial cluster detection and classification through product density LISA functions
Version: 0.1.1
Nickname: Coffee Aroma
Date: 2015-10-01
Author: Francisco J. Rodriguez-Cortes and Jonatan A. Gonzalez
Maintainer: Francisco J. Rodriguez-Cortes <cortesf@uji.es>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2),
    splancs,
    KernSmooth,
    spatstat,
    astsa
Description: Basic toolkit for cluster detection in spatial point patterns through local versions of the second-order product density function wich seting a powerful tool to address the problem of classification. The LISA functions can then be grouped into bundles of similar local behaviour using multivariate hierarchical clustering techniques according to a particular statistical distances.
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1